{"tid":1788550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【都市擂台】爭議聲大，警隊加薪應否分拆審議？","createTime":"2019-12-18T18:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T23:41:17.000Z","uid":313166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7d39b913b86337e40b07c440f92deafa83d9fca8","tid":1788550,"uid":313166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T18:14:37.000Z","msg":"Yahoo 係19左啲<br />\n但有票唔係唔投呀嘛<br />\n冇理由咁易俾班曱甴加薪!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/poll/575dfc60-217c-11ea-a73c-893dbc610387\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fpoll%2F575dfc60-217c-11ea-a73c-893dbc610387&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6ubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=93df1efe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/poll/575dfc60-217c-11ea-a73c-893dbc610387</a>"},{"pid":"48ff72d14197b7c8caa51c2be2c389f8d4611aaa","tid":1788550,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T18:15:33.000Z","msg":"請推po<br />\n<br />\n【核彈】呢個方法可以防水炮車【行動po求推】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n稅局行動宣言：<br />\n<br />\n稅局，納稅人金錢吐納之處。六月以降，香港警隊搬出大量催淚彈、布袋彈、橡膠子彈甚或實彈，一一射向香港市民。購置武器，所費不菲，警隊資金何來？稅款必是一大來源。港人金錢，變作供養濫暴警隊的薪水，變作不人道武器還於港人之身，這絕非稅款的正當用途。政府無能，特首執拗難以平息民憤，何解需公帑埋單？<br />\n<br />\n香港市民安分守己，繳納血汗金錢；今民意所指為五大訴求，政府乃人民公僕，理應善用公帑以平眾怒，藉稅款促進訴求之達成以撫民心。然林鄭政府恣意調用港人金錢，屢行政治操作，維護腐敗議會，投稅款入朽壞警隊之血海，廣大市民如何甘心將夙夜辛勞所得，雙手奉上予這毫無公信力的政府？<br />\n<br />\n我等市民將一連三星期到稅局抗議，以示港人之怒，不到五大訴求悉數落實一日不熄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6ubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=1bbac3e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6ubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=2e05eb29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a>"},{"pid":"3441e7d219a28c0f5c55bdbe518196fc0a45c15e","tid":1788550,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T18:25:48.000Z","msg":"消防吊手岩殉職案　休班警認見「勿前進」牌照行　遭斥害了很多人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1076936\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1076936</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">唔知呢個害死人嘅休班狗<br />\n最近過成點</span></span>"},{"pid":"d0a5971cec8334fb0a18068ccf2016dad9675be2","tid":1788550,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T23:41:17.000Z","msg":"香港地投票 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人唔可以再慣性沉默🈲❌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1784354\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1784354</a>"}]}